                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d532">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 838.00/1198.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Chargé <persName type="from">Davis</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Port au Prince</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-06-20">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 20, 1915</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Government forces took Cape Haitien yesterday. Revolutionary forces retreated
                    into the woods. Considerable firing and sailors of the <hi rend="italic"
                        >Descartes</hi> landed.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Davis</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
